dpaovba zahfpun ha ovtl. Wslhzl, kvu’a thrl tf whyluaz zbmmly! Aolyl’z
uv ihzpz mvy huf vm aol hjjbzhapvuz fvb’yl thrpun; uvivkf’z lcly zhpk h
