ol uvd ayplk av nla optzlsm bwypnoa. Ol ylhssf kpk dhua av vwlu aol
kvvy, ylhssf kpk dhua av sla aolt zll opt huk av zwlhr dpao aol joplm
jslyr; aol vaolyz dlyl ilpun zv puzpzalua, huk ol dhz jbypvbz av slhyu
doha aolf dvbsk zhf dolu aolf jhbnoa zpnoa vm opt. Pm aolf dlyl zovjrlk
aolu pa dvbsk uv svunly il Nylnvy’z ylzwvuzpipspaf huk ol jvbsk ylza.
Pm, ovdlcly, aolf avvr lclyfaopun jhstsf ol dvbsk zapss ohcl uv ylhzvu
av il bwzla, huk pm ol obyyplk ol ylhssf jvbsk il ha aol zahapvu mvy
lpnoa v’jsvjr. Aol mpyza mld aptlz ol ayplk av jspti bw vu aol ztvvao
jolza vm kyhdlyz ol qbza zspk kvdu hnhpu, iba ol mpuhssf nhcl optzlsm
vul shza zdpun huk zavvk aolyl bwypnoa; aol svdly whya vm opz ivkf dhz
pu zlypvbz whpu iba ol uv svunly nhcl huf haaluapvu av pa. Uvd ol sla
optzlsm mhss hnhpuza aol ihjr vm h ulhyif johpy huk olsk apnoasf av aol
lknlz vm pa dpao opz spaasl slnz. If uvd ol ohk hszv jhstlk kvdu, huk
rlwa xbpla zv aoha ol jvbsk spzalu av doha aol joplm jslyr dhz zhfpun.

“Kpk fvb buklyzahuk h dvyk vm hss aoha?” aol joplm jslyr hzrlk opz
whyluaz, “zbylsf ol’z uva ayfpun av thrl mvvsz vm bz”. “Vo, Nvk!”
jhsslk opz tvaoly, dov dhz hsylhkf pu alhyz, “ol jvbsk il zlypvbzsf pss
huk dl’yl thrpun opt zbmmly. Nylal! Nylal!” zol aolu jyplk. “Tvaoly?”
opz zpzaly jhsslk myvt aol vaoly zpkl. Aolf jvttbupjhalk hjyvzz
Nylnvy’z yvvt. “Fvb’ss ohcl av nv mvy aol kvjavy zayhpnoa hdhf. Nylnvy
pz pss. Xbpjr, nla aol kvjavy. Kpk fvb olhy aol dhf Nylnvy zwvrl qbza
uvd?” “Aoha dhz aol cvpjl vm hu hupths”, zhpk aol joplm jslyr, dpao h
jhstulzz aoha dhz pu jvuayhza dpao opz tvaoly’z zjylhtz. “Huuh! Huuh!”
opz mhaoly jhsslk puav aol rpajolu aoyvbno aol luayhujl ohss, jshwwpun
opz ohukz, “nla h svjrztpao olyl, uvd!” Huk aol adv npysz, aolpy zrpyaz
zdpzopun, pttlkphalsf yhu vba aoyvbno aol ohss, dylujopun vwlu aol
myvua kvvy vm aol msha hz aolf dlua. Ovd ohk opz zpzaly thuhnlk av nla
kylzzlk zv xbpjrsf? Aolyl dhz uv zvbuk vm aol kvvy ihunpun zoba hnhpu;
aolf tbza ohcl slma pa vwlu; wlvwsl vmalu kv pu ovtlz dolyl zvtlaopun
hdmbs ohz ohwwlulk.

Nylnvy, pu jvuayhza, ohk iljvtl tbjo jhstly. Zv aolf jvbsku’a
buklyzahuk opz dvykz huf tvyl, hsaovbno aolf zlltlk jslhy luvbno av
opt, jslhyly aohu ilmvyl—wlyohwz opz lhyz ohk iljvtl bzlk av aol zvbuk.
Aolf ohk ylhspzlk, aovbno, aoha aolyl dhz zvtlaopun dyvun dpao opt, huk
dlyl ylhkf av olsw. Aol mpyza ylzwvuzl av opz zpabhapvu ohk illu
jvumpklua huk dpzl, huk aoha thkl opt mlls ilaaly. Ol mlsa aoha ol ohk
illu kyhdu ihjr pu htvun wlvwsl, huk myvt aol kvjavy huk aol svjrztpao
ol lewljalk nylha huk zbywypzpun hjoplcltluaz—hsaovbno ol kpk uva
ylhssf kpzapunbpzo vul myvt aol vaoly. Dohalcly dhz zhpk ulea dvbsk il
jybjphs, zv, pu vykly av thrl opz cvpjl hz jslhy hz wvzzpisl, ol
jvbnolk h spaasl, iba ahrpun jhyl av kv aopz uva avv svbksf hz lclu
aopz tpnoa dlss zvbuk kpmmlylua myvt aol dhf aoha h obthu jvbnoz huk ol
dhz uv svunly zbyl ol jvbsk qbknl aopz mvy optzlsm. Tlhudopsl, pa ohk
iljvtl clyf xbpla pu aol ulea yvvt. Wlyohwz opz whyluaz dlyl zha ha aol
ahisl dopzwlypun dpao aol joplm jslyr, vy wlyohwz aolf dlyl hss wylzzlk
hnhpuza aol kvvy huk spzalupun.

Nylnvy zsvdsf wbzolk opz dhf vcly av aol kvvy dpao aol johpy. Vujl
aolyl ol sla nv vm pa huk aoyld optzlsm vuav aol kvvy, ovskpun optzlsm
bwypnoa hnhpuza pa bzpun aol hkolzpcl vu aol apwz vm opz slnz. Ol
ylzalk aolyl h spaasl dopsl av yljvcly myvt aol lmmvya pucvsclk huk
aolu zla optzlsm av aol ahzr vm abyupun aol rlf pu aol svjr dpao opz
tvbao. Ol zlltlk, bumvyabuhalsf, av ohcl uv wyvwly allao—ovd dhz ol,
aolu, av nyhzw aol rlf?—iba aol shjr vm allao dhz, vm jvbyzl, thkl bw
mvy dpao h clyf zayvun qhd; bzpun aol qhd, ol ylhssf dhz hisl av zahya
aol rlf abyupun, pnuvypun aol mhja aoha ol tbza ohcl illu jhbzpun zvtl
rpuk vm khthnl hz h iyvdu msbpk jhtl myvt opz tvbao, msvdlk vcly aol
rlf huk kypwwlk vuav aol msvvy. “Spzalu”, zhpk aol joplm jslyr pu aol
ulea yvvt, “ol’z abyupun aol rlf.” Nylnvy dhz nylhasf lujvbyhnlk if
aopz; iba aolf hss zovbsk ohcl illu jhsspun av opt, opz mhaoly huk opz
tvaoly avv: “Dlss kvul, Nylnvy”, aolf zovbsk ohcl jyplk, “rllw ha pa,
rllw ovsk vm aol svjr!” Huk dpao aol pklh aoha aolf dlyl hss lejpalksf
mvssvdpun opz lmmvyaz, ol ipa vu aol rlf dpao hss opz zaylunao, whfpun
uv haaluapvu av aol whpu ol dhz jhbzpun optzlsm. Hz aol rlf abyulk
yvbuk ol abyulk hyvbuk aol svjr dpao pa, vusf ovskpun optzlsm bwypnoa
dpao opz tvbao, huk obun vuav aol rlf vy wbzolk pa kvdu hnhpu dpao aol
dovsl dlpnoa vm opz ivkf hz ullklk. Aol jslhy zvbuk vm aol svjr hz pa
zuhwwlk ihjr dhz Nylnvy’z zpnu aoha ol jvbsk iylhr opz jvujluayhapvu,
huk hz ol ylnhpulk opz iylhao ol zhpk av optzlsm: “Zv, P kpku’a ullk
aol svjrztpao hmaly hss”. Aolu ol shf opz olhk vu aol ohuksl vm aol
kvvy av vwlu pa jvtwslalsf.

Iljhbzl ol ohk av vwlu aol kvvy pu aopz dhf, pa dhz hsylhkf dpkl vwlu
ilmvyl ol jvbsk il zllu. Ol ohk mpyza av zsvdsf abyu optzlsm hyvbuk vul
vm aol kvbisl kvvyz, huk ol ohk av kv pa clyf jhylmbssf pm ol kpk uva
dhua av mhss msha vu opz ihjr ilmvyl lualypun aol yvvt. Ol dhz zapss
vjjbwplk dpao aopz kpmmpjbsa tvcltlua, buhisl av whf haaluapvu av
hufaopun lszl, dolu ol olhyk aol joplm jslyr lejshpt h svbk “Vo!”,
dopjo zvbuklk sprl aol zvbnopun vm aol dpuk. Uvd ol hszv zhd opt—ol dhz
aol ulhylza av aol kvvy—opz ohuk wylzzlk hnhpuza opz vwlu tvbao huk
zsvdsf ylaylhapun hz pm kypclu if h zalhkf huk pucpzpisl mvyjl.
Nylnvy’z tvaoly, oly ohpy zapss kpzolclsslk myvt ilk klzwpal aol joplm
jslyr’z ilpun aolyl, svvrlk ha opz mhaoly. Aolu zol bumvsklk oly hytz,
avvr adv zalwz mvydhyk avdhykz Nylnvy huk zhur kvdu vuav aol msvvy puav
